creator: PRINC
descriptionHtml:
With the baby widget, you can automatically check your baby's age,
as well as his or her weeks, months, and memorable dates every day
just by registering your child's birthday or due date.

With the status bar and widget tools, you can check everything without running the app, and our notifications will help you always remember important dates.


Keep track of your pregnancy stages!
You can check the months, weeks, days left in your pregnancy, as well as personalized information about your baby.


Information about each of your baby's development stage!
We provide you with custom information about childcare for each development stage,
and we send you a special card for each memorable day!


Calendar and baby diary functions as well!
Your diary will be accessible easily according to days, weeks, and months. You can also use our stickers to decorate your diary.


Secure data protection!
Even if you have a new phone, your data will be safely restored through our cloud backup system.


All functions are easy to use, and accessible at a glance.
Check all information about your baby easily and always be happy and healthy with our baby widget!

With the baby widget, you can automatically check your baby's age,
as well as his or her weeks, months, and memorable dates every day
just by registering your child's birthday or due date

With the status bar and widget tools, you can check everything without running the app, and our notifications will help you always remember important dates


Keep track of your pregnancy stages
You can check the months, weeks, days left in your pregnancy, as well as personalized information about your baby


Information about each of your baby's development stage
We provide you with custom information about childcare for each development stage,
and we send you a special card for each memorable day


Calendar and baby diary functions as well
Your diary will be accessible easily according to days, weeks, and months. You can also use our stickers to decorate your diary


Secure data protection
Even if you have a new phone, your data will be safely restored through our cloud backup system


All functions are easy to use, and accessible at a glance
Check all information about your baby easily and always be happy and healthy with our baby widget


Data is stored in https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com when using cloud backup.
Storage user data
- Email, app data, photo
